sequenceDiagram
actor Client as User
participant API as Presentation(API)
participant Facade as HBnBFacade
participant BLL as BusinessLogic(SearchService)
participant PlaceRepo as Persistence(PlaceRepository)

Client->>API: GET /places?min_price&max_price&lat&long&radius&amenity_ids
API->>API: Validate query params (types, ranges)
API->>Facade: list_places(filters)

Facade->>BLL: list_places(filters)
BLL->>BLL: validate_filters(filters)
BLL->>BLL: normalize_filters(filters)\n(defaults, bounds)

BLL->>PlaceRepo: search(filters)
PlaceRepo-->>BLL: list of places

BLL-->>Facade: places DTO list
Facade-->>API: 200 OK
API-->>Client: 200 [{id,title,price,lat,long,amenities},...]